CommitMessage:
Merge pull request #117 from rtavenar/dev-tests

[MRG] Moved depreacted code from barycenters to deprecated (road to 0.2)

Add girder_client to setup.py (#868)

* Add girder_client to setup.py

* Update requirements-dev.txt

* Unpin virtualenv.

virtualenv 20.0.21 fixes the issue we had; remove the period in the tox
install command also avoids it somehow.

* Do a simple test of the wheels.

Allow circleci to run on Python 3.8 and fix issues with the 3.6 and 3.7
environments.

Change code that will break on 3.8.
